g.text: [[option != 0] In case the actor wishes to filter the catalog again]
[In case the actor wishes to choose another presentation order]
[option != 0 (If the actor wishes more than one option)]
[option != 0 (if the actor wishes more than one option)]
4.1: Asks the actor if he wishes to filter the catalog again
3.4: Asks the actor if he wishes to select another presentation order of the catalog
3: Selects the presentation order of the catalog
2.2: Shows all the presentation order options and asks to select one (eg.growing/descending production code, growing/descending name...)
1.2: Presents all the possible filter options (brand,description,status,category... , or even without a filter option)
2: Filters the catalog choosing the desired filter options
1: Requests to see the products catalog
